# This dir is mounted as the container's ~/.claude, so Claude writes its runtime
# state here (projects/, todos/, statsig/, shell-snapshots/, history, credentials,
# settings.local.json). Whitelist: ignore everything, then re-include the tracked
# config so new runtime files are ignored by default.
*
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!settings.json
!hooks/
!hooks/**
hooks/**/__pycache__/
!modes/
!modes/**
!skills/
!skills/**
